就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：改善抗爭能力，提升身份認同<br />\n建議：各有各做，best effort <br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化民主陣營勢力<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n衛城革命,生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡,打倒腐敗<br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值/level</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考5.精通專業技能6.低消費、高儲蓄<br />\n<strong><em>每日任務：</em></strong>1.幫襯良心商店、抵制送中商戶2.開AC玩國際戰線 (Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)3.多發佈正面資訊、冷處理負面POST4.十點咆哮發泄5.思考完就take action<br />\n<strong><em>每星期任務</em></strong>：1. 罷買日2. 教育家中兩老3. 去連儂牆幫手4.參加一樣民主活動5. 諗下點樣爭取民主<br />\n<strong><em>每月任務</em></strong>：1. 換美金，走資2. 陪審員/派傳單/放映會/各有各做<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=502ddec4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=064006de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=2872777b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.09.27<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要記住極權如何打壓香港示威：</span></strong><br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨<br />\n2.誤導：送中條例、說謊、黃色object等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n10.扮好人/扮對話：「江山易改本性難移」<br />\n諗到再加</span>"},{"pid":"1b69a4a513aef474ca5cc2187fe64a4229bcc105","tid":1598230,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1952528b8b6a307fd98cb441de3fce194c5f9ace","tid":1598230,"uid":45797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:13:20.000Z","msg":"岩岩收工 黎緊"},{"pid":"6d33b0afbcc47775f4e7ea0af0e6556d89fee372","tid":1598230,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:13:53.000Z","msg":"過緊黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0676c78e8a4451b35e9f1847fa97e7f99255d6c7","tid":1598230,"uid":91484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:14:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"578104c64977fb92d91cd64be748b481b0667404","tid":1598230,"uid":106604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919609fefa9ef916b87de095741205456839fd76","tid":1598230,"uid":50692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"屌 去錯遮打個post都多人過呢個認真post<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\